WEBVTT

00:00:00.587 --> 00:00:03.500
Ljudska vrsta je u centru 
pažnje na TED-u,

00:00:03.670 --> 00:00:06.483
ali želio bih dodati 
i glas za životinja,

00:00:07.313 --> 00:00:12.442
čija su nas tijela i umovi 
i duhovi oblikovali.

00:00:13.112 --> 00:00:16.358
Prije nekoliko godina, imao sam sreće

00:00:16.358 --> 00:00:18.306
sresti starješinu plemena na otoku

00:00:18.306 --> 00:00:20.200
nedaleko od Vancouvera.

00:00:20.860 --> 00:00:22.818
On se zove Jimmy Smith,

00:00:23.238 --> 00:00:25.167
i ispričao mi je priču

00:00:25.487 --> 00:00:27.840
koja se priča u njegovom narodu,

00:00:27.840 --> 00:00:31.035
koji sebe zovu Kwikwasut'inuxw.